The man's eyes widened in horror as Albino seized him by the throat and dragged him out forcefully into the open, tearing a hole into the wall in the process, his fate sealed in an instant as Albino crushed his head with a sickening crunch.
In another encounter, a soldier attempted to grapple with Albino, his desperation evident in every movement. But Albino was a force of nature, his strength unmatched and his resolve unyielding. With a swift motion, he dismembered the soldier with brutal efficiency, leaving him to crumple to the ground in a heap of broken limbs and shattered dreams.
